ISNOW PATTERN SHOWCASE	ISNOW("pat") is TRUE when the isnow pattern holds at the current clock — the column changes every recompute; patterns are verbatim from the tsvsheet/isnow conformance corpus
Pattern	Holds now?	Means
--- SYMBOLS: WEEKDAY NAMES (case-insensitive, minimal-unique) ---
M noon	=isnow("M noon")	Monday at 12:00:00
Tu noon	=isnow("Tu noon")	Tuesday at noon
Th noon	=isnow("Th noon")	Thursday at noon
Su noon	=isnow("Su noon")	Sunday at noon
monday noon	=isnow("monday noon")	case-insensitive: same as "M noon"
Wednesday noon	=isnow("Wednesday noon")	full weekday name also resolves
MWF noon	=isnow("MWF noon")	the run Mon/Wed/Fri, at noon
SS noon	=isnow("SS noon")	the weekend run (Sat+Sun), at noon
TT noon	=isnow("TT noon")	the run Tue+Thu, at noon
M	=isnow("M")	Monday — every minute (bare weekday leaves time wild)
Sa	=isnow("Sa")	Saturday — every minute
Su	=isnow("Su")	Sunday — every minute
*/*/* 2 12:00	=isnow("*/*/* 2 12:00")	numeric weekday 2 = Monday (Sun=1); numeric form needs all three groups
*/*/* 7 12:00	=isnow("*/*/* 7 12:00")	numeric weekday 7 = Saturday, at 12:00
--- SYMBOLS: TIME NAMES ---
noon	=isnow("noon")	12:00:00
midnight	=isnow("midnight")	00:00:00
midday	=isnow("midday")	synonym for noon
mn	=isnow("mn")	abbreviation for midnight
md	=isnow("md")	abbreviation for midday
n	=isnow("n")	unique prefix of the three time words: noon
--- STRUCTURE: THE SHORTHAND LADDER (short pattern -> canonical form) ---
6	=isnow("6")	bare hour: 06:00:00 daily
/1 18	=isnow("/1 18")	the 1st of any month at 18:00
Su :0,30	=isnow("Su :0,30")	Sundays at :00 and :30 of every hour
12/-1 0	=isnow("12/-1 0")	last day of December at 00:00
2000// ::0+[5]	=isnow("2000// ::0+[5]")	year 2000, every 5th second
*	=isnow("*")	the bare star: every minute
12/25	=isnow("12/25")	December 25, every minute that day
:0,30	=isnow(":0,30")	minute set :00 and :30 — hour left wild
2026//	=isnow("2026//")	any instant in the year 2026
7/14	=isnow("7/14")	one slash = month/day: July 14
2 :30	=isnow("2 :30")	a bare number fills the empty hour slot: 02:30
M.noon	=isnow("M.noon")	"." is a group separator: same as "M noon"
M_noon	=isnow("M_noon")	"_" is a group separator too
" 6 "	=isnow(" 6 ")	surrounding separators tolerated (a pattern is one shell-safe token)
M,W,F noon	=isnow("M,W,F noon")	weekday set Mon/Wed/Fri, at noon
*/*/15 4 12:00	=isnow("*/*/15 4 12:00")	day 15 AND weekday 4 (Wed) — fields AND together
*/*/15 5 12:00	=isnow("*/*/15 5 12:00")	day 15 AND weekday 5 (Thu) — both must hold
*/*/* 2-6 12:00	=isnow("*/*/* 2-6 12:00")	numeric weekday span Mon–Fri, at 12:00
*/*/* 2+[1] 12:00	=isnow("*/*/* 2+[1] 12:00")	numeric-weekday step: 1st Monday, at 12:00
--- FIELD ALGEBRA: WILDCARD, EXACT, SET, EXCLUSION, SPAN, FROM-END, STEP ---
*/*/* * *:00:00	=isnow("*/*/* * *:00:00")	wildcard hour: every hour, on the hour
2026// *:*:00	=isnow("2026// *:*:00")	exact year 2026, every minute
/1,4,7,10/ *:*:00	=isnow("/1,4,7,10/ *:*:00")	month set Jan/Apr/Jul/Oct, every minute
:00,15,30,45	=isnow(":00,15,30,45")	minute set: every quarter hour
/!1 *:*:00	=isnow("/!1 *:*:00")	field exclusion: every day except the 1st
8-12	=isnow("8-12")	hour span 08–12 inclusive, on the hour
M-F noon	=isnow("M-F noon")	weekday span Monday–Friday, at noon
22-2	=isnow("22-2")	hour span that wraps midnight: 22:00–02:00
*/*/29-* *:*:00	=isnow("*/*/29-* *:*:00")	day span open at the top: the 29th onward
*/*/-1 *:*:00	=isnow("*/*/-1 *:*:00")	from-end: the last day of the month
*/12/-15 *:*:00	=isnow("*/12/-15 *:*:00")	the last 15 days of December
*/12/-2w1d *:*:00	=isnow("*/12/-2w1d *:*:00")	from-end unit compound: last 2 weeks 1 day of December
:0+[15]	=isnow(":0+[15]")	step: every 15 minutes from :00
::+[9]	=isnow("::+[9]")	step: every 9 seconds
:-[15]	=isnow(":-[15]")	descending minute step counted from the end: :59, :44, :29, :14
Monday+[3] noon	=isnow("Monday+[3] noon")	the 3rd Monday of the month, at noon
11/ Th-[1] noon	=isnow("11/ Th-[1] noon")	the last Thursday of November, at noon
M+[1,3] noon	=isnow("M+[1,3] noon")	the 1st and 3rd Monday, at noon
/+[3w] noon	=isnow("/+[3w] noon")	week-granular: every 3rd week of the year, at noon
M+[1],W+[2] noon	=isnow("M+[1],W+[2] noon")	set distributes the step: 1st Monday and 2nd Wednesday, at noon
M-F-[1] noon	=isnow("M-F-[1] noon")	weekday-span BYSETPOS: last business day of the month, at noon
M-F+[1] noon	=isnow("M-F+[1] noon")	first business day of the month, at noon
--- INTERVALS: "EVERY N UNITS", CROSSING FIELD BOUNDARIES ---
+[90mn]	=isnow("+[90mn]")	every 90 minutes (re-aligns at the day boundary)
+[2h]	=isnow("+[2h]")	every 2 hours
+[3d]	=isnow("+[3d]")	every 3 days (week-anchored)
+[25h]	=isnow("+[25h]")	every 25 hours (walks across the week)
+[10d]	=isnow("+[10d]")	every 10 days within the month
+[40d]	=isnow("+[40d]")	every 40 days within the year
+[30s]	=isnow("+[30s]")	every 30 seconds
M-F +[90mn] >=6 <=18	=isnow("M-F +[90mn] >=6 <=18")	every 90 min, weekdays only, 06:00–18:00 (interval ANDed with weekday + bounds)
--- PATTERN-LEVEL EXCLUSIONS: "! spec" CARVES INSTANTS OUT ---
M-F ! 12/25	=isnow("M-F ! 12/25")	every weekday except December 25
noon ! 12/25 ! 1/1	=isnow("noon ! 12/25 ! 1/1")	noon daily, except Christmas and New Year's (a holiday list)
noon ! 12/25	=isnow("noon ! 12/25")	noon daily, except December 25
M-F !12/25	=isnow("M-F !12/25")	no space: "!12/25" binds as a field exclusion, NOT a whole-day skip
--- BOUNDS & WINDOWS: SINCE (>, >=) / UNTIL (<, <=) ---
12 >=2011	=isnow("12 >=2011")	hour 12, only from year 2011 onward
12 <9/1	=isnow("12 <9/1")	hour 12 daily, until September 1 (exclusive)
::+[9] >=6 <=18	=isnow("::+[9] >=6 <=18")	every 9 seconds, within the 06:00–18:00 window
12 >=2011 <2016	=isnow("12 >=2011 <2016")	hour 12, bounded to years 2011–2015
::+[7] >=6 <=7	=isnow("::+[7] >=6 <=7")	continuous stepping: every 7 seconds in 06:00–07:00, restarting each day
